<SYNC Start=4422400><P Class=EGCC>
He was a deserter.
<SYNC Start=4423700><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=4424900><P Class=EGCC>
Do you have to rake everything up?
<SYNC Start=4426600><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=4427200><P Class=EGCC>
What are you going to do, <br>
